com.kontakt.sdk.android.http

Class ETag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.http.ETag

  • public final class ETag
extends java.lang.Object
    ETag is introduced to provide web cache validation and to allow to make conditional requests. Its primal aim is to enable more efficient collaboration with REST API as a web server does not need to send a full response if the content has not changed.
